snippet: Dane Piedt became the second South African in 126 years to take a wicket with his first ball in test cricket but said it was not his most memorable scalp of the day and that he could have played better....

headline.print_headline: South Africa's Piedt Excels on Debut, Says More to Come
headline.main: South Africa's Piedt Excels on Debut, Says More to Come

lead_paragraph: Dane Piedt became the second South African in 126 years to take a wicket with his first ball in test cricket but said it was not his most memorable scalp of the day and that he could have played better.
